<p><strong>Building Type:</strong> Academic</p>
<p><strong>Current Use:</strong> Grosvenor Hall is located in the West Green, coordinates E-4 on the campus map. It is marked as #123 on the map.<br/><br/>The building houses the Graduate College, Office of Information Technology, Vice President for Research, Culinary, Anatomy class labs, and university Flexspaces.</p>
<p><strong>Building Directory:</strong> <a href="https://www.ohio.edu/building-directory/grosvenor-hall">https://www.ohio.edu/building-directory/grosvenor-hall</a></p>]]>
