<p><strong>Building Type:</strong> Mixed Use</p>
<p><strong>Current Use:</strong> The Kennedy Museum of Art is located in Lin Hall, located on The Ridges.<br/><br/>The Kennedy Museum of Art enhance the intellectual and cultural life of Ohio University and the region through quality national and international exhibitions, collection-based research, and diverse formal and informal learning opportunities.</p>
