<p><strong>Building Type:</strong> Mixed Use</p>
<p><strong>Current Use:</strong> Lin Hall is located on The Ridges, across the Hocking River from the Convocation Center, between coordinates C-7 on the campus map. It is marked as #201 on the map.<br/><br/>Lin Hall, located on The Ridges, houses the Kennedy Museum of Art and Ohio University Museum Complex.</p>
